---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI Strategy & Transformation" description="From 'we should do something with AI' to a strategy your board can fund.">

  <PageHero
    label="Services"
    title='From "we should do something with AI" to a strategy your <span class="text-ms-green-400">board can fund.</span>'
    subtitle="Most companies don't fail at AI because the technology isn't ready. They fail because they never built the bridge between opportunity and execution."
  />

  <!-- Phases -->
  <section class="bg-ms-dark-800 border-y border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 space-y-20">

      <!-- Phase 1 -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] gap-8">
        <div>
          <p class="text-ms-green-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Phase 1</p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">2–3 weeks</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">AI Readiness Assessment</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-6">Before we talk about what AI <em>could</em> do, we figure out what your organization <em>can</em> do.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-400">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-ms-green-400">→</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Technology & data audit: What systems do you run? What data do you have, and how clean is it?</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-ms-green-400">→</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Process mapping: Where are the bottlenecks, the manual work, the decisions made on instinct?</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-ms-green-400">→</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Culture & skills assessment: How AI-ready is your team? Where's the resistance?</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-ms-green-400">→</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Competitive scan: What are your competitors doing with AI?</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-8 bg-ms-dark-700 rounded-xl p-4 border border-white/5">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Deliverable</p>
            <p class="text-white font-medium">AI Readiness Report. A clear picture of where you stand, where the gaps are, and what's realistic.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-white/5"></div>

      <!-- Phase 2 -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] gap-8">
        <div>
          <p class="text-ms-green-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Phase 2</p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">3–4 weeks</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Use Case Identification & Business Case</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-6">The graveyard of AI projects is full of technically impressive solutions to problems nobody had.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-400">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-ms-green-400">→</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Structured use case discovery: Workshops with leadership and operational teams</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-ms-green-400">→</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Prioritization: Business value vs. feasibility vs. risk. No pet projects.</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-ms-green-400">→</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Business case development: Expected ROI, investment, timeline, risks</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-ms-green-400">→</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Build vs. buy analysis: When to use off-the-shelf, when to build custom, when to wait</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-8 bg-ms-dark-700 rounded-xl p-4 border border-white/5">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Deliverable</p>
            <p class="text-white font-medium">AI Strategy Document. A prioritized roadmap with business cases your CFO can actually approve.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-white/5"></div>

      <!-- Phase 3 -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] gap-8">
        <div>
          <p class="text-ms-green-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Phase 3</p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">Ongoing</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Implementation Support</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-6">Strategy without execution is a PDF that gathers dust.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-400">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-ms-green-400">→</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Pilot design: Scope, success criteria, kill criteria</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-ms-green-400">→</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Vendor selection: Technology-agnostic. We help you pick what works.</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-ms-green-400">→</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Change management: Training, communication, getting buy-in</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-ms-green-400">→</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Progress reviews: Regular check-ins to course-correct early</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-8 bg-ms-dark-700 rounded-xl p-4 border border-white/5">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Deliverable</p>
            <p class="text-white font-medium">A running AI pilot with measurable results, not another proof of concept.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Differentiators -->
  <section class="bg-ms-dark-900">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12">What makes this different.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">We've built AI products.</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Not just strategy decks. Our founder led Beethoven X, one of the most ambitious AI creativity projects in history. We know what it takes to go from idea to something real.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">We don't sell implementation.</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">If you need a systems integrator, we'll help you find the right one. We're not trying to extend the engagement. We're trying to make you self-sufficient.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">We speak executive, not engineer.</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">You'll never hear us say "fine-tune a transformer model on your proprietary corpus." You'll hear "here's what this means for your margin."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA />

</Layout>
